Music composition overall is brilliant. Hats off for the raag by Akbar Ali. Arieb Azhar needs little more improvement on Punjabi poetry pronunciation. QB sung it nicely but her singing style, as if she's drunk, doesn't sound good to ears at some points.
Overall Great Track. Thumbs up String. This will definitely go to my playlist.
